streamdown-native
Copyright Dark Research contributors

This project began from the streamdown-rn package in darkresearch/generative-ui
(https://github.com/darkresearch/generative-ui).

Its native primitives and theme conventions were informed by shadcn/ui
(https://ui.shadcn.com) and Base UI (https://base-ui.com). No browser-specific
component implementation from those projects is bundled by this package.

This product includes parity metadata derived from the test-suite names and
layout of Vercel Streamdown (https://github.com/vercel/streamdown), pinned at
commit e5deed330aa4231751a106445d93d62e4716a22f and licensed under Apache-2.0.
The corresponding source snapshot is reproducibly identified in
parity/upstream.json; it is not included in the published package.

The native streaming animation design was informed by the MIT-licensed tail
animators in Software Mansion's react-native-enriched-markdown
(https://github.com/software-mansion/react-native-enriched-markdown).
